<graph edgedefault="undirected"><node id="B客戶">
  <data key="d0">B客戶</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">B клиент (B客戶) is an organization or company that receives maintenance services and for whom detailed maintenance records are maintained. B клиент consistently appears in descriptions as a recipient of maintenance activities, with specific emphasis on the comprehensive documentation of these interactions and services provided to them. Maintenance records for B клиент include various aspects of service history, ensuring thorough and detailed tracking of all maintenance-related actions performed on their behalf. These records serve as a critical resource for ongoing support and historical reference, covering all maintenance activities conducted for B клиент. The descriptions uniformly indicate that B клиент is both a customer and a client for whom comprehensive maintenance records are kept, underscoring the importance of these documents in providing continuous service and support.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e2a0171ee9d19cc664d4d041d3e73ba2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0d3b88d3601a1081c8354e0ef27952f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe7268a7cb94439d483759e501068db6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-daa296a353c26f41dfc613743d24e936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-75fa98905e1d68515f390e75c46adddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e6e1908b68b82814f06780675f7938b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-39206ec5906f23d68e051b1df74d3ca7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-412e17859c430b9ce8b929bc152053ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d96ca3133c54d9d76add7de434ee05b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f62a98ad02d11a4c9618cbda43281859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72f381579d364fa91cc3e73153e0af97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2940790b50eb2cba2a5e944b95a94dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04465635a6b88183cbabbfe7e25635dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942b136689124792272bc32a2898842c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84c3e0271089b72556be831ea38a055f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3</data>
