<node id="E客戶">
  <data key="d0">E客戶</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">E客戶 is an entity representing both an organization and a customer, whose maintenance records are meticulously documented. E客户 receives ongoing support from engineers, including on-site assistance when necessary. The primary documentation related to E 고객 focuses on maintenance activities and service interactions, ensuring comprehensive record-keeping for future reference and support continuity. Maintenance services provided to E客戶 include those conducted by C人员 and involve the use of Splunk for monitoring and maintaining systems. E客户 is a client that uses Splunk and requires regular maintenance services, emphasizing its role as both an organization and a customer in receiving detailed and continuous support.&lt;SEP&gt;E客戶is a client organization for whom maintenance work was conducted.&lt;SEP&gt;E客戶is a client organization for which maintenance records are kept, involving Splunk software.&lt;SEP&gt;E客戶is a client entity for which maintenance records are kept.&lt;SEP&gt;E客戶is the client for whom maintenance records are kept.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-738a58105cbf665748b3257e0cfee9ac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-996c8aba3ce4de0e9bb90c0d569231f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d02e98febcd8f8650bbe77d789a41d69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cafeb58d25cc4cbc85eaf07cf415496a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-76068a2f95fd89e7ceb4741d4eb478ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5096c0cdf6972a3670732e4f9be1d36a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0add79f46581b83deba682a2c89cdb7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fcc4bf66788ce00c23c3e736753ea50a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0c6684aa00106f16e7869f519061642&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a40e782f3c3804da0a1d45dfa05eefe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25d7c29d65aa0e4d54fb4af54207fa0d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e6839b81653aa7c9b7ec794f3447380&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6f1e5469f6278ea8a34bff96b293b69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0640212d45b4b92d91d0255cf90edf96&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1df6d8d113790f99d50593095e1e5e58&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0cef05272158ef916c2b84f625b2ddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c4967b23b72f04d5c4ef37149d21ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8bddb98b4a84e394c0a4558b42ae12d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0cd3e323fc2a43e461d7af757b08706</data>
