<node id="Carbon-Fiber Spikes">
  <data key="d0">Carbon-Fiber Spikes</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Carbon-Fiber Spikes are advanced sprinting shoes designed to enhance the performance of athletes by providing both increased speed and superior traction. Made from carbon fiber, these shoes offer a lightweight yet durable construction that supports high-performance sprinters during competitive events. Descriptions highlight their suitability for athletes such as Noah Carter, emphasizing their role in improving athletic capabilities through optimized design features.&lt;SEP&gt;Carbon-fiber spikes are advanced sprinting shoes used by athletes to enhance performance.&lt;SEP&gt;Advanced sprinting shoes made of carbon fiber that provide enhanced speed and traction.&lt;SEP&gt;Carbon-fiber spikes are advanced sprinting shoes that provide enhanced speed and traction.&lt;SEP&gt;Advanced sprinting shoes made of carbon fiber that provide enhanced speed and traction.&lt;SEP&gt;Advanced sprinting shoes that provide enhanced speed and traction, used by Noah Carter to break the 100m sprint record.&lt;SEP&gt;Advanced sprinting shoes that provide enhanced speed and traction used by Noah Carter to break the 100m sprint record.</data>
