<node id="A部門">
  <data key="d0">A部門</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-daa296a353c26f41dfc613743d24e936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d96ca3133c54d9d76add7de434ee05b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f62a98ad02d11a4c9618cbda43281859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2940790b50eb2cba2a5e944b95a94dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942b136689124792272bc32a2898842c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3</data>
  <data key="d2">A部門 is a department within an organization responsible for carrying out various maintenance activities. It plays a crucial role in performing maintenance tasks specifically related to the systems of B客戶, including those involving Splunk. The department handles multiple aspects of system maintenance and has been involved in resolving anomalies related to user roles in Splunk. Additionally, A部門 is mentioned in maintenance records as being responsible for handling specific tasks associated with maintaining the integrity and functionality of various systems within the organization.&lt;SEP&gt;A department is a section within B客戶's organization where certain maintenance tasks are performed.&lt;SEP&gt;A department that completed an account inventory check and sent a report to C同事.&lt;SEP&gt;A部門is a department where account audit and confirmation were completed and sent to Hank.</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773783897</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="B部門">
  <data key="d0">B部門</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-daa296a353c26f41dfc613743d24e936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d96ca3133c54d9d76add7de434ee05b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f62a98ad02d11a4c9618cbda43281859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2940790b50eb2cba2a5e944b95a94dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942b136689124792272bc32a2898842c</data>
  <data key="d2">B部門 is a department that plays a significant role in various maintenance activities. It is particularly involved in the processes related to FISAC data collection, containment, and SH KVstore engine testing. The department also handles specific tasks such as IP application submission and anomaly testing for the KVstore engine. Additionally, B部門 is responsible for Splunk maintenance tasks and has been mentioned in several maintenance records for its involvement in various technical duties. B部門 works closely with B客戶 on FISAC data collection activities and ensures the smooth operation of relevant systems through these diverse responsibilities.&lt;SEP&gt;B department is another section within B客户的组织，执行特定的维护任务。&lt;SEP&gt;B department is involved in ongoing tasks such as FISAC data collection and SH KVstore engine anomaly testing.</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773783838</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="FISAC資料收容-進行中">
  <data key="d0">FISAC資料收容-進行中</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2940790b50eb2cba2a5e944b95a94dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942b136689124792272bc32a2898842c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3</data>
  <data key="d2">FISAC資料收容-進行中 refers to an ongoing process within the FISAC system that involves multiple tasks related to data containment and submission. This process includes submitting IP applications through APIs for specific IP addresses in the FISAC system. The ongoing task requires API requests to be made, typically involving a request to a colleague (B同事) to submit the necessary IP application. Additionally, it encompasses various activities such as collecting and containing data within FISAC systems. These tasks are part of an integrated project that aims to ensure proper management and submission of data through designated APIs for specific IP addresses.</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773783910</data>
