  <data key="d2">Testing for the abnormal status of SH KVstore engine is in progress within a personal test environment.&lt;SEP&gt;#Ongoing SH KVstore engine anomaly testing in a personal test environment.&lt;SEP&gt;SH KVstore引擎異常測試-進行中indicates a test being conducted on SH's KVstore engine status within a personal testing environment.&lt;SEP&gt;SH KVstore engines are being tested for anomalies, indicating ongoing troubleshooting efforts.&lt;SEP&gt;An ongoing test of the SH KVstore engine for anomaly detection.&lt;SEP&gt;An ongoing test in the personal testing environment to check SH's KVstore status.&lt;SEP&gt;SH KVstore engine anomaly testing is an ongoing test conducted in a personal testing environment.</data>
