<edge source="B客戶" target="A人員">
  <data key="d7">15.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(A人員, B клиент) is a relationship where A人員 performs various maintenance tasks on behalf of B клиент. This role includes executing specific maintenance work and managing the overall maintenance records and services needed by B клиент. A人员 ensures that any issues or requirements related to system maintenance are addressed promptly. The responsibilities of A人員 encompass both carrying out maintenance activities and overseeing the process to ensure continuous support and service quality for B клиент.

The relationship involves A人員 providing comprehensive maintenance services tailored to meet B客户的 needs, including executing specific tasks and maintaining detailed records. This ensures that B клиент receives continuous and high-quality maintenance support from A人员. The descriptions consistently highlight that A人员 executes maintenance work for B客戶's systems and manages the associated service requirements effectively.</data>
