<edge source="B客戶" target="C人員">
  <data key="d7">15.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(B客戶, C人員) refers to a relationship where C人員 provides comprehensive maintenance and technical support services for B客戶. This partnership involves handling various maintenance issues related to B客户的 systems, including problems with IDX hard disk space and data synchronization. The responsibilities of C人员 include providing regular preventive maintenance to avoid potential system issues and resolving any existing technical difficulties faced by B客户 promptly.

C人员 also serves as a point of contact for ongoing support during specified time periods, ensuring that the needs of B客戶 are met through continuous service provision. This relationship highlights the ongoing partnership between C人员 and B客户 in maintaining and improving the performance of B客户的 systems. Additionally, C人員 is responsible for executing maintenance work and providing services to maintain system functionality and stability.

C personnel's duties extend beyond reactive problem-solving; they also engage in proactive measures such as regular service checks to prevent potential issues from arising, thereby ensuring that B客戶’s needs are consistently addressed with high-quality support and service provision.</data>
