C人员 has conducted on-site maintenance at E客户的 facility, indicating their involvement in direct physical support alongside remote service provision. This engagement is characterized by continuous service delivery intended to maintain and enhance the functionality of E客户的 systems through both routine maintenance and specialized support. The relationship underscores a dedicated commitment from C人员 to fulfill all maintenance needs of E客户, ensuring their operational efficiency and system reliability.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員handles maintenance for E客户的Splunk system as part of their responsibilities.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員provides maintenance and support services for E客戶's systems or equipment.&lt;SEP&gt;Maintenance records are kept for E客戶by C人員.</data>
