<edge source="C客戶" target="B人員">
  <data key="d7">15.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(B人员, C客户) represents a relationship where B人员 provide comprehensive maintenance and technical support services to C客户. Specifically, B人员 offer various maintenance services that include handling service requests related to C客户的 Splunk SIEM system. These services are provided during specified periods and encompass both the provision of maintenance work and technical support. The descriptions indicate that B人员 have consistently offered these services in multiple instances, ensuring continuous support for C客户's technological needs. Additionally, B人员 are responsible for managing records and documentation related to maintenance tasks for C客戶.

B人员负责处理针对C客户的维护工作，包括提供维修服务和技术支持。这些服务旨在满足C客户的技术需求，并确保其技术系统的稳定运行。B人员不仅负责日常的维护任务，还承担了与维护相关的记录和文档管理工作，以保障服务质量的一致性和透明度。</data>
  <data key="d9">engineering support,maintenance,maintenance service,maintenance support,maintenance work,responsibility,service provider,service provision,support interaction,technical support</data>
