<edge source="Quarterly Earnings Report" target="Nexon Technologies">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The negative impact on Nexon Technologies' stock was due to lower-than-expected results in their latest quarterly earnings report.&lt;SEP&gt;The release of Nexon Technologies' quarterly earnings report affected the company's stock value and overall market perception.&lt;SEP&gt;Nexon Technologies released a quarterly earnings report that led to significant stock declines due to disappointing results.</data>
